peanut butter and coconut collagen oats!
yes, i'll add collagen peptides to just about anything! i do it for my hair, skin, digestion and a healthy gut 🙋🏻 doesn't taste like anything and it adds some good ol protein so i'm #winning. do it.
3/4C sprouted oats (i buy the @sproutedflour oats from @wholefoods), 1C @erewhonmarket coconut milk, cinnamon, @vitalproteins collagen peptides, 1Tbs @philosophielove superfood coconut butter, @wedderspoonofficial manuka honey, a banana and LOTS of @wild_friends pb. don't measure. the serving size is just a lame suggestion. i don't buy into it 🤷🏻‍♀️
